comments: Drummond (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Clarkson's (UTA) path and absorbs the contact.
Ilyasova (UTA) beats Caldwell-Pope (LAL) to the spot and establishes himself in a legal guarding position prior to Caldwell-Pope initiating contact.
Horton-Tucker (LAL) engages and disengages with O'Neale (UTA) along the perimeter.
Morris (LAL) and Ilyasova (UTA) engage and disengage with one another along the perimeter.
Ilyasova (UTA) and Caldwell-Pope (LAL) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Morris (LAL) establishes a screening position in Clarkson's (UTA) view and gives Clarkson room to avoid the contact.
Schroder (LAL) uses his left hand to ward off Ilyasova's (UTA) left arm and affects Ilyasova's ability to contest the driving shot attempt.
O'Neale (UTA) establishes a screening position in Horton-Tucker's (LAL) path and absorbs the contact.
Schroder (LAL) firms up in his defensive position and absorbs the body contact made with Clarkson (UTA) in the post.
Schroder (LAL) makes contact with the ball and incidental "high-five" contact with Clarkson (UTA) during his jump shot attempt.
Morris (LAL) establishes a screening position in O'Neale's (UTA) view and gives O'Neale room to avoid the contact, which Morris absorbs.
Schroder (LAL) extends his hand forward and initiates contact with Clarkson's (UTA) front that affects his SQBR.
Kuzma (LAL) extends his hand forward and marginal contact occurs with O'Neale's (UTA) back during the layup attempt. Morris (LAL) legally contests O'Neale's layup attempt.
Morris (LAL) establishes a screening position in O'Neale's (UTA) view and gives O'Neale room to avoid the contact. Morris and O'Neale engage and disengage thereafter.
Caruso (LAL) makes incidental contact with Bogdanovic's (UTA) left hand/wrist as they each attempt to gain control of the rebound.
Ingles (UTA) and Kuzma (LAL) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Schroder (LAL) has his hand rested on Clarkson's (UTA) hip and quickly removes it as Clarkson moves through the lane toward the perimeter.
O'Neale (UTA) is moving somewhat laterally toward Schroder (LAL) when marginal body contact occurs after Schroder's gather.
Schroder (LAL) moves alongside Clarkson's (UTA) path and marginal body contact occurs during Clarkson's dribble.
Schroder (LAL) extends his hand forward and marginal contact occurs with Clarkson (UTA) during his shot attempt.
